de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.application

Class AbstractApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.application.AbstractApplication
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CacheDoubleDistanceInOnDiskMatrix, CacheDoubleDistanceKNNLists, CacheDoubleDistanceRangeQueries, CacheFloatDistanceInOnDiskMatrix, ClassifierHoldoutEvaluationTask, ComputeKNNOutlierScores, ConvertToBundleApplication, EvaluateIntrinsicDimensionalityEstimators, EvaluatePrecomputedOutlierScores, GeneratorXMLSpec, GreedyEnsembleExperiment, KDDCLIApplication, MiniGUI, MultiStepGUI, PrecomputeDistancesAsciiApplication, VisualizeGeodesicDistances, VisualizePairwiseGainMatrix

    public abstract class AbstractApplication
extends java.lang.Object
    AbstractApplication sets the values for flags verbose and help.

    Any Wrapper class that makes use of these flags may extend this class. Beware to make correct use of parameter settings via optionHandler as commented with constructor and methods.

    Since:
    0.2
    Author:
    Elke Achtert, Erich Schubert
